        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Scope 3 Act </strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits any requirement that an issuer of securities must disclose the greenhouse gas emissions of its value chain (i.e., scope 3 emissions). </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
